The paper focuses on face recognition using deep convolutional networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses transfer learning and regularization techniques, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of large datasets and web-scale training is also mentioned, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) in terms of data privacy and security.
